---
title: Marry Me Chicken Penne with Sun-Dried Tomatoes & Scallions
description: This dish is so delicious, we think it could inspire proposals, plus it’s quick and easy to boot—ready in just 20 minutes! The sauce is a combo of sun-dried tomatoes, cream cheese, chicken stock, garlic, butter, and chiles. It’s rich and creamy, but with a bright, addictive sun-dried tomato tang. It’s draped over juicy seared chicken and tender penne.
